attributes.review: I downloaded the app as a joke to pass time, and looking back it was a horrible mistake. Because as soon as I did it IMMEDIATELY asked for my phone number. Being the bored person I am I said “why not?” And then I got asked for my email. “Why not” as soon as I verified my phone number and email I kept getting calls THREATENING to kill me if I don’t vote for trump. And I got spam emails. I will copy them here “ Dear,                 Thanks for downloading my app. Now revote for me. Or I will come to your house and dance on your kitchen table like a anorexic Cheeto puff.” I said “ :0” but again thought nothing of it as I continued to get spam calls and emails I heard a ring on my doorbell. Not even a second later THE Donald j trump BURST through my door wearing an ill-fitting Cheeto puff costume and started dancing on my kitchen table. He then proceeded to bash my 26 month old daughters head in. (She died later in the hospital 😢🕊) he then proceeded to try and attack me. Luckily John cena came through my wall and said “are you sure about that?” And he killed Donald trump with my butterknife. Overall terrible experience and customer service. -100000/10 would not recommend.

attributes.review: i downloaded this app so i could help with trumps campaign, the first thing it asks is for my phone number, i assumed it was just for the verification code, it was at first, but later on i started receiving about 9 messages per minute from the number just saying to help with his campaign. i then later started receiving more text but instead of being about his campaign, i was getting death threats and receiving pictures of my own house. i am absolutely terrified and infuriated that, our president, Donald Trump, is allowing his app to run this way.
